	section#about.flex.collapse-col
		div.flex.full
			h1 Hey, I'm Sarvesh!
			img(src='../images/headshot.png')
			#links.flex.f-row
				a(href='TODO'
						rel='noopener noreferrer',
						target='_blank')
					img(src='../images/resume.svg')
				a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/sarvesh-kalwit/'
						rel='noopener noreferrer',
						target='_blank')
					img(src='../images/linkedin.svg')
				a(href='https://github.com/sarveshkalwit'
						rel='noopener noreferrer',
						target='_blank')
					img(src='../images/github.svg')
				a(href='https://medium.com/@sarveshkalwit'
						rel='noopener noreferrer',
						target='_blank')
					img(src='../images/medium.svg')
				a(href='https://soundcloud.com/sarvesh_kalwit'
						rel='noopener noreferrer',
						target='_blank')
					img(src='../images/soundcloud.svg')
				a(href='#contact')
					img(src='../images/email.svg')
				a(href='TODO'
						rel='noopener noreferrer',
						target='_blank')
					img(src='../images/instagram.svg')
				
		div.flex.full
			p
				| I was born and raised in the Silicon Valley, and I'm currently
				| pursuing undergraduate degrees in computer science and math at 
				a(href='https://www.utexas.edu/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') The University of Texas at Austin
				| . Alongside my classes, I'm an Incubator lead at 
				a(href='https://www.txconvergent.org/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') Texas Convergent 
				| and the Technology Director at the 
				a(href='https://www.texasakpsi.com/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') Iota chapter 
				| of Alpha Kappa Psi. After graduation, I hope to work at a disruptive
				| technology company.
			p
				| I'm largely interested in software engineering, technical product 
				| management, stock prediction, and venture capitalism.
				| My main technical skills include Python, fullstack JavaScript, and 
				| Java.
			p
				| In my free time, I enjoy lifting weights, working on side projects, 
				| reading, watching standup comedy, producing music, exploring new 
				| places, and hanging out with friends.
		
